commit message:
Do not export AboutActivity

This commit fixes potential fragment injection vulnerability.
Fix invalid AboutActivity's parent activity name
Add missing contentDescription to ImageView in properties_list_item layout
Bump target SDK version to version 20
RTL: Do not change text direction
build_db.py: Fix parsing of superscripts in articles
Use static version of gradle plugin

ZoomableScrollView: Do not use initializeScrollbars()

initializeScrollbars() is deprecated in API 21.

Bump target SDK version

Use API 21 (Android 5.0) as target API.
Always use exact versions of dependencies
Bump target SDK version in AndroidManifest
ElementsAdapter: Fix a crash on a filter being applied while the list was empty
